                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-1230" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES DAWSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a watchman of Woolwich. I received information, and went in pursuit of the prisoner—I found him going into the Three Daws public-house—he had two pairs of trowsers on, which I took to Mr. Moore.</p>
